1. **STATE_DEVICE_ON** : Animation for this page is done and fixed _do not touch it_
2. **STATE_DEVICE_SCREENSAVER** : Infinit Animation for this page is done just few minor improvements is needed here 
    - Change the color of explosion to yellow for vibrate and red for explosion (not done yet)
    - Need to Add a long press B action for this (not done yet)
3. **STATE_DEVICE_MENU** : This page was done but right now i changed the whole plan for the device so pages are done. Just i will rework on those pages according to the new features
4. **STATE_TIMER_SELECT_TIME** : Right now there will be no timer functionality overall so the timer and the rest of the timer pages will be kept as it or hidden
9. **STATE_THEMES** : The feature of this page will be changed all together to Color Flood or Chromatic Spread. This will be interactive color spreading based on the button presses. I will change the name of the state too **STATE_COLOR_FLOOD** 
10. **STATE_BRIGHT** : The feature of this page will be changed to Falling Pixel. This will be interactive each button presses will drop a pixel and when all the pixel are filled then a dramatic animation to clear all the pixel , the name of this state change to **STATE_FALLING_PIXEL**